review_blob: Well it has some kick. A little too sour and not a great palate. Not my first choice.
Great taste of Guinness. very similar tastes great pleasing aroma. nice beer.
Wonderfull hops and dark flavor. Similar to the draught but alittle stronger. Good pallet and excellent aroma.
Great Vienna! The head is ok. The taste is amasingly smooth and no nasty after tastse. One of the best dark beers I have had. If you get a chance try one I think you will enjoy it
Great Lager.  I was very impressed, went down smooth, no bad aftertaste and overall nice beer, not bad for a long neck. Can't wait to down a draught. Good balance between taste and ABV! ;)
